Pull over the car on the side of the road
Use the handbrake to prevent the car from movement
Turn off the car
Take out the switch
Put the switch in your right pocket
Open the door
Get out of the car
Close the door
Get to the back of the car
Open the trunk
Search for jack, wrench, spare tire
Take the jack and spare tire and wrench
take them all with you
Go to the flat tire
Use the jack to push the car up
Open all the lug nuts of the flat tire with the wrench
Replace the flat tire with the spare tire
Close all the lug nuts with the wrench
Release the jack
Put the flat tire, wrench, and the jack back in their places
go to the drivers seat
open the door
sit
close the door
take out the switch from your right pocket
start the car
drive
